  <content>This macro adds a checkboxed **task with checkbox** macro and an event listener for ticking completed tasks off using the checkboxes

**Example:**

{{checktask dueDate="31.12.2022, 23:59:59"}}
Description of task to be done
{{/checktask}}

**CKEditor:**

In order to make best use of it, add the following CKeditor configuration to your editor through the [[dedicated "WYSIWYG Editor" section&gt;&gt;url:https://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/CKEditor%20Integration/#HAdministrationSection]] in the [[Wiki Administration&gt;&gt;url:https://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/Administration%20Application]]:

{{code language="javascript" layout="LINENUMBERS"}}
config['xwiki-macro'] = config['xwiki-macro'] || {};
config['xwiki-macro'].insertButtons = [
  {
    insertDirectly: false,
    macroCall: {
      name:'checktask',
      inline:'enforce',
    }
  }
];
{{/code}}

**Macros and components:**

* [[Checkboxed Task&gt;&gt;CheckboxedTask]]: Contains the **checktask **macro that inserts checkboxed tasks in pages and a JavaScript listener that listens for checking/unchecking events
* [[Task Listener&gt;&gt;doc:Macros.CheckboxedTask.Code.TaskListener]]: Event listener that listens for creating and updating tasks on pages, adding XObjects to the respective pages
* [[Task Updater&gt;&gt;doc:Macros.CheckboxedTask.Code.TaskUpdater]]: Is called by the JavaScript listener to update the XObject of a task when checked or unchecked
* [[Task Class&gt;&gt;doc:Macros.CheckboxedTask.Code.TaskClass]]: XObject class that defines the properties of tasks to be saved
* [[Task Report Macro&gt;&gt;doc:Macros.CheckboxedTask.Code.TaskReportMacro]]: Contains the macro **reportchecktasks **that inserts a task report in pages using the default **live data** macro. Also contains another JavaScript listener listening for checking/unchecking events within the live data table.
* [[Task JSON&gt;&gt;doc:Macros.CheckboxedTask.Code.TaskJSON]]: Defines the database query and formats the input for the live data macro in the task report
* [[Translations&gt;&gt;doc:.Code.Translations]]: Contains the localized labels of the task and task report macros</content>
